{"tid":1571950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位勇武巴打做得好","createTime":"2019-09-15T14:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:41:01.000Z","uid":154299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f77476f4606df1580a1eb3e357f0c4be5e3f1dc","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"Popo已經唔可信<br />\n有事只可以靠自己<br />\n有黑社會 廢老 藍絲 福建幫 乜都好<br />\n人數就係一切<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十則圍之，五則攻之，倍則分之；敵則能戰之，少則能守之，不若則能避之。故小敵之堅，大敵之擒也。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n夠人當然要打柒佢<br />\n<br />\n最好打到佢失去還手嘅能力<br />\n久而久之 俾人打多幾次<br />\n佢就會覺得自己作為藍絲<br />\n生出來就係要俾你打嘅<br />\n打到佢哋懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔認同巴打私了既你<br />\n寧願你走 都唔好做阻膠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說：唔好打 唔好變成對家一樣<br />\n只著說：不完美 可接受</span></span><br />\n然後開遮幫手cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aafc755871fc0a3d0a88ce56008a165db8f6066","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"6月果陣 我仲會on99覺得狗有好人<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了"},{"pid":"eb3d4dc06def79cafc9fe2c8faf599ca18b8f04a","tid":1571950,"uid":27871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"不完美 可接受 錫埋春袋就完美"},{"pid":"99fd14b10aaada8c454fdaa49d7ec76c594005eb","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"如果有和理非同你持不同嘅意見<br />\n佢哋反對私了嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n不要屌柒佢地on9道德撚<br />\n試著說：下次我地幫手做掩護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢佢地就會接受"},{"pid":"8db14ae61121ade132d789e4afba14082fc3ac1b","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"同跳閘一樣 <br />\n唔好指責比錢搭車既人<br />\n唔好怪佢地<br />\n<br />\n試著教佢地點樣唔比錢搭<br />\n花式過閘<br />\n「跳」既心理關口太大<br />\n就由捐/跟/廢老卡開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好一昧鬧<br />\n要慢慢導佢地成材"},{"pid":"ef91c0aeca1b0dcdc8a8448b398eaa72338a6ba9","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"勇務和理非一條心<br />\n光復香港指日可待"},{"pid":"121c99fc58d8b55bf43576131baa3ca8f9ee9ee4","tid":1571950,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c9a97790ce1c721e6da714bbde83dbbb036df0b","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"推一百次<br />\n1/100"},{"pid":"487251b99d32da005b69ed41a2ab17ebf197f7ee","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"再自推 2/100"},{"pid":"7a3ea18b5d92a58238d9946fd39da172a6983cbb","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"再自推 3/100"},{"pid":"41724a8109e1db04b74507f3280bdb05064b71fa","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"係戰勝既思考法則<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5767d9f1d33835590653e3bdd94ac604f8612a15","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"再推 4/100"},{"pid":"97520b50daf3798cd65b97847b7cda6411e38b28","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:37:01.000Z","msg":"畀人捉到，唔好驚唔好荒，無論捉你既係市民、粉衫定黃衫，請企定定大聲講：<br />\n<br />\n「港鐵元朗站唔關車門，太子站封站，日日派車運警察，賺賺埋埋香港咁多錢！轉頭幫手打香港人！沙中線啲螺絲扭返好未！跳閘係表態！」<br />\n<br />\n記住要大聲講出黎，一黎要話畀身邊其他香港人知我地點解要咁做，二黎要嚇一嚇對方，對方見你咁大聲，好少再繼續捉住你，我已經咁樣走甩兩次。當然如果畀狗捉，請乖乖地交罰款，唔好同狗糾纏。<br />\n<br />\n原文 <br />\n█ █ █ █ █有冇跳閘都入黎聽我講兩句，唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8f499ec8461ba1b98108abe19fa37a77758ab9c","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"畀人捉到，唔好驚唔好荒，無論捉你既係市民、粉衫定黃衫，請企定定大聲講：<br />\n<br />\n「港鐵元朗站唔關車門，太子站封站，日日派車運警察，賺賺埋埋香港咁多錢！轉頭幫手打香港人！沙中線啲螺絲扭返好未！跳閘係表態！」<br />\n<br />\n記住要大聲講出黎，一黎要話畀身邊其他香港人知我地點解要咁做，二黎要嚇一嚇對方，對方見你咁大聲，好少再繼續捉住你，我已經咁樣走甩兩次。當然如果畀狗捉，請乖乖地交罰款，唔好同狗糾纏。<br />\n<br />\n原文 <br />\n█ █ █ █ █有冇跳閘都入黎聽我講兩句，唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b1840c16966917de671a9eae86996028f3da7ef","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z07oYHJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ07oYHJ.png&h=e1ed2f22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/di2oYHK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdi2oYHK.png&h=5bb67401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要改變思考模式<br />\n唔好互相指責 試着引導對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566adde5fa18b564cec0b6ae1b2de52a104321f6","tid":1571950,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"好 8/100 推"}]}